cvs.texi(,910)  |   |    |
cvs.texi(,911)  |   |    +--@t{CVSROOT}
cvs.texi(,912)           |      (administrative files)
cvs.texi(,913)           |
cvs.texi(,914)           +--@t{gnu}
cvs.texi(,915)           |   |
cvs.texi(,916)           |   +--@t{diff}
